headline: Ross Stores Announces Quarterly Dividend
summary: DUBLIN, Calif., November 20, 2024--Ross Stores, Inc. (Nasdaq: ROST) announced today that the Company’s Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $0.3675 per common share, payable on December 31, 2024 to stockholders of record as of December 10, 2024.

headline: Target Sinks To New Low On Holiday Gloom After Huge Earnings Miss
summary: Target earnings came in well below views, with the discounter slashing guidance, in sharp contrast to rival Walmart. Target stock dived.
